<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> July 7, 2026</p>

<p>Comic Craft Studios ("we", "our", or "us") values your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our mobile applications and services.</p>

<h2>Information We Collect</h2>

<ul>
<li>Device information</li>
<li>Operating system and device model</li>
<li>App usage analytics</li>
<li>Crash reports</li>
<li>Subscription and purchase information processed by Apple or Google</li>
<li>Information you voluntarily provide when contacting support</li>
</ul>

<p>We do not collect personally identifiable information unless you voluntarily provide it.</p>

<h2>How We Use Information</h2>

<ul>
<li>Improve app performance</li>
<li>Provide customer support</li>
<li>Fix bugs and crashes</li>
<li>Analyze app usage</li>
<li>Process subscriptions and purchases</li>
<li>Maintain app security</li>
</ul>

<h2>Third-Party Services</h2>

<p>Our applications may use trusted third-party services including:</p>

<ul>
<li>Google Play Services</li>
<li>Google Analytics for Firebase</li>
<li>Firebase Crashlytics</li>
<li>Google AdMob (where applicable)</li>
<li>AppLovin MAX (where applicable)</li>
<li>AppsFlyer (where applicable)</li>
<li>Apple App Store</li>
<li>Google Play Billing</li>
</ul>

<p>These services may collect information according to their own privacy policies.</p>

<h2>Advertising</h2>

<p>Some of our applications may display advertisements provided by trusted advertising partners. Subscription-only apps may not display advertisements.</p>

<h2>Subscriptions</h2>

<p>Subscriptions and in-app purchases are securely processed through Apple App Store or Google Play. We do not collect or store payment information.</p>

<h2>Children's Privacy</h2>

<p>We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe a child has provided personal information, please contact us.</p>

<h2>Data Security</h2>

<p>We use reasonable security measures to protect your information. However, no method of electronic transmission or storage is completely secure.</p>

<h2>Your Rights</h2>

<p>Depending on your country or region, you may have the right to access, correct, delete, or restrict the use of your personal information.</p>

<h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>

<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>

